snippet.title: Family Party Fitness Fun - Wii - Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out Family Trailer Fitness Fun, the latest in up to 4-player sporting antics which include 30 Fitness Fun games made for kids

Play with your friends or family on a Balance Board  or test yourself in the 1VS mode.

And we got all the exciting sports which include: Sky diving, Trampolining, Dodgeball, Roller derby, Paintball, Tug of war, Basketball shootout... AND MUCH MORE!

For more info, go to: http://www.namcobandaigames.eu
